---
title: Cheese Tortellini in a Turkey Tomato Sauce with Roasted Peppers and Spinach
description: Tortellini brings a speedy and cheesy twist to pasta night! We've put a delicious, wholesome spin on our rich tomato sauce by adding ground turkey, roasted red peppers and spinach.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheese-tortellini-in-a-turkey-tomato-sauce-ef6b43b0.jpg
